00040 - (NSMethodSignature *)methodSignatureForSelector:(SEL)aSelector {
00041         if ([self respondsToSelector:aSelector]) {
00042                 return [super methodSignatureForSelector:aSelector];
00043         }
00044         
00045         [self.should exist:[NSString stringWithFormat:@"before you can call %@", NSStringFromSelector(aSelector)]];
00046         NSString *selector = NSStringFromSelector(aSelector);
00047         
00048         //Check if any view responds directly to selector
00049         for (UIView *target in [self targetViews]) {
00050                 if ([target respondsToSelector:aSelector]) {
00051                         return [target methodSignatureForSelector:aSelector];
00052                 }
00053         }
00054         
00055         //Check if any view responds as a property match
00056         NSArray *selectors = [selector componentsSeparatedByString:@":"];
00057         if (selectors.count == 2) {
00058                 return [[self with] methodSignatureForSelector:aSelector];
00059         }
00060 }

00125 - (UIQuery *)touch {

00127         
00128         for (UIView *view in [self targetViews]) {
00129                 UITouch *touch = [[UITouch alloc] initInView:view];
00130                 UIEvent *eventDown = [[NSClassFromString(@"UITouchesEvent") alloc] initWithTouch:touch];
00131                 NSSet *touches = [[NSMutableSet alloc] initWithObjects:&touch count:1];
00132                 
00133                 [touch.view touchesBegan:touches withEvent:eventDown];
00134                 
00135                 UIEvent *eventUp = [[NSClassFromString(@"UITouchesEvent") alloc] initWithTouch:touch];
00136                 [touch setPhase:UITouchPhaseEnded];
00137                 
00138                 [touch.view touchesEnded:touches withEvent:eventDown];
00139                 
00140                 [eventDown release];
00141                 [eventUp release];
00142                 [touches release];
00143                 [touch release];
00144                 [self wait:.25];
